column5: Klaus Stern Credit  I found this on the Algonquin Adventures mb, and it seems to capture some of the magic of the park.  75 more sleeps until the May trip.  I know, it's a little depressing, but it will only get better.
Nice link Doug. Although I'm enjoying the hardwater action right now, I too am looking forward to the ritual trip into Algonquin for spring lakers.  GR
